premise_source_doc_sentence: Caitlyn Marie Jenner  (  born October 28 , 1949  )  , formerly known as Bruce Jenner , is an American television personality and retired Olympic gold medal-winning decathlete .
It also features their parents Kris and Caitlyn Jenner  (  previously known as Bruce Jenner  )  , and brother Rob Kardashian .
Caitlyn Jenner  (  born 1949 ; birth name William Bruce Jenner  )  , American television personality , athlete , and LGBT rights activist
